********************************************************
*                                                      *
* Instructions to compile and run GPU RawToCPE package *
*                                                      *
* Output: ClusterId  xhit(in cm)  yhit(in cm)          *
* This are stored in the device memory for further use *   
*                                                      *
********************************************************

Input file: /home/fpantale/data/920/PU50/085D5AAF-9E40-E711-B12A-0025905A609E.root

1. login to felk40
   > ssh username@lxplus.cern.ch
   > ssh felk40

2. Download the code from repository
   > cmsrel CMSSW_9_2_0
   > cd src
   > cmsenv
   > git cms-merge-topic sushildubey171:GPU_RawToCPE_NEvents
   > scram setup /home/fpantale/cuda_8.0.44.xml
   > scram b -j8

3. Run 
   > cd /EventFilter/SiPixelRawToDigi/test
   > cmsRun runRawToCPE_GPU_phase1.py   
   
